About Us
Celery City Craft — Inspired by Sanford’s Heritage
Celery City Craft isn’t just a bar—it’s a celebration of Sanford’s heritage and a lively gathering place for locals and visitors alike. Nestled in Historic Downtown Sanford, Florida, we offer a unique blend of craft beer, cocktails, live music, and mouthwatering food, all in a community-focused setting.
History
Our Name, Our Story
Sanford was once known as the “Celery Capital of the World,” thanks to its thriving celery farms in the early 20th century. We honor this local legacy with our name,
Celery City Craft
, and a décor that showcases the town’s rich history. From vintage photos to nods to Sanford’s agricultural roots, our space is infused with the spirit of the community we love.
Learn More
Community
Outreach & Connection
Celery City Craft is built on a passion for supporting the local community. From partnering with animal rescues to hosting fundraisers and community events, we aim to make a positive impact on Sanford. Our commitment to preserving the town’s unique history and fostering connections is at the heart of everything we do.
Learn More
Where Community and Craft Collide.
Celery City Craft isn’t just a bar—it’s a celebration of Sanford’s heritage and a lively gathering place for locals and visitors alike. Nestled in Historic Downtown Sanford, Florida, we offer a unique blend of craft beer, cocktails, live music, and mouthwatering food, all in a community-focused setting.
Since 2014, we’ve proudly established ourselves as Sanford's favorite spot for friends to gather and stories to unfold.
FAQ
Celery City Craft —Frequently asked questions
At Celery City Craft, we aim to provide a seamless experience for our guests. Whether you’re curious about our offerings, hours, or events, you’ll find the answers to some of our most frequently asked questions below. If you have any other questions, don’t hesitate to reach out!
What are your hours of operation?
We are open Wednesday to Monday from 11 AM to 12 AM, and Thursday to Saturday from 11 AM to 2 AM. For specific holiday hours, please check our social media.
Where is Celery City Craft located?
We’re located at 114 S Palmetto Ave, Sanford, FL 32771, in Historic Downtown Sanford.
Do you host live music or events?
Yes! We regularly host live music, trivia nights, and special events. Check out our events calendar on our website or follow us on social media for the latest updates.
Is Celery City Craft pet-friendly?
Absolutely! We love our furry friends. Well-behaved dogs are welcome on our outdoor patio area. Just make sure they’re on a leash and kept under control.
Do you have food options available?
Enjoy mouthwatering dishes from our partner, Sushi & Seoul, located on the patio. Indulge in a variety of options including fresh sushi, Korean fried chicken, potstickers, and much more!
